title: DumpsterGun
body:
The dumpster seems to be filled with an assortment of documents associated with TempestTech.
There is also other, smellier, things.
[[Rummage through the bin some more|DumpsterGun.Rummage]]
[[Jump in for a more thorough, dirtier search|DumpsterGun.Search]]
[[It's probably nothing. Walk away.|DumpsterGun.Exit]]

title: DumpsterGun.Rummage
body:
You start moving some of the documents and rubbish around, you find a half eaten pizza.
<<thinkingFont Dialogue>>
Why would anyone throw this away?
<<endThinkingFont Dialogue>>
[[Eat a slice of the pizza|DumpsterGun.Pizza]]
[[Jump in the dumpster|DumpsterGun.Search]]
[[Leave, there's nothing worthwhile here|DumpsterGun.Exit]]

title: DumpsterGun.Search
body:
You jump into the dumpster.
You feel around the contents with your hands and legs.
You kick something hard, reaching in you pull out a rifle.

title: DumpsterGun.Pizza
body:
You eat the slice of pizza. It has anchovies, gross.
[[Jump in the dumpster|DumpsterGun.Search]]
[[Leave, there's nothing worthwhile here|DumpsterGun.Exit]]
